{
  "texts": [
    "We then performed a hallucination index accuracy check to assess how well our model mitigates one of the biggest challenges for LLMs.",
    "We introduce three versions of our model.",
    "Firstly, FinTral-INST is our instruction-fine-tuned model obtained by fine-tuning our pre-trained model.",
    "Note that we do not assess the performance of the pre-trained model as it serves as an intermediate step to the instruction fine-tuning model.",
    "Secondly, We introduce FinTral-DPO, which has been further trained based on FinTral-INST utilizing reinforcement learning using AI feedback with the dDPO objective."
  ]
}